    </div>
    <div class="scope out-of-scope">OUT OF SCOPE</div>
    <p>
        In addition to Pricing Tables, Pricing Strategy can contain Terms and Conditions related to the Pricing Table.
        These Terms and Conditions generally effect how the deals are created and/or effect the deals workflow.
        Idealy, these Terms and Conditions can be user managed and created to map the changes to the deals automatically.
        For the Term and Conditions that cannot be automated or simply haven't been created for the automated process, the user can manually fix the deals prior to approving them.
    </p>
    <div>
        <img src="/images/docs/terms.png" style="margin-top: 10px;" />
    </div>


    <a href="#" name="Contract"></a>
    <h4 style="margin-top: 25px;">Contract</h4>
    <div style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
        <i class="fa fa-certificate" aria-hidden="true" style="font-size: 30px; color: #0071c5;"></i>
        <i class="fa fa-key" aria-hidden="true" style="font-size: 25px; color: #cccccc; margin-left: 5px;"></i>
