        Customers formally agree to the Pricing Strategies in the form of a Contract created outside of MyDeals.
        The Rebate Strategies are presented to the custer using C2a, DocuSign or SharePoint.
        At this time, the expectation is to remain outside of MyDeals, but in the future, this should be integrated into the tool as an automated step.
    </p>
